- cs.CL (Computational Linguistics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses language learning and the use of example sentences to improve language proficiency. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper leverages the GiveMeExample system, which uses machine learning algorithms to suggest example sentences. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to suggest example sentences. 
- cs.ED (Education) is a possible category as the paper discusses a method for improving language learning. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the use of a computer system to assist language learning.
